OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital, but sadly
OL,7,Fdied three days later, on 29 May,
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Police said.
OL,10,FIn a tribute to the landscape
OL,11,Fgardener, who worked in West Scotland,
OL,12,Fhis mother Jo, who appeared with him
OL,13,Fin the BBC travel competition in 2019,
OL,14,Fand his father Andrew, said he was
OL,15,F"loyal, funny and fiercely protective".
OL,17,F"We are devastated by the loss of our
OL,18,Fbeloved son Sam in a terrible
OL,19,Faccident," they said.
