OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'loyal and
OL,4,Cfunny' Race Across the World contestant
OL,6,F"Sam left us far too soon, and whilst
OL,7,Fwords will never fully capture the
OL,8,Flight, joy and energy he brought into
OL,9,Four lives, we hold on to the memories
OL,10,Fthat made him so special.
OL,12,F"Sam was adored by his family. As a
OL,13,Fson, brother and nephew, he was loyal,
OL,14,Ffunny and fiercely protective.
OL,16,F"He did Race Across The World in 2019,
OL,17,Fwhich opened his eyes to the wonder of
OL,18,Fadventure and travel. He was willing
OL,19,Fto go wherever the trail might lead
OL,20,Fand he touched everyone he met on the
OL,21,Froad.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
