OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'loyal and
OL,4,Cfunny' Race Across the World contestant
OL,6,F"He found great happiness working as a
OL,7,Flandscape gardener on the west coast
OL,8,Fof Scotland.
OL,10,F"Sam brought warmth, laughter and a
OL,11,Fsmattering of chaos wherever he went.
OL,12,FHe leaves behind a huge hole in our
OL,13,Fhearts.
OL,15,F"We will miss him endlessly, but we'll
OL,16,Falso remember him with smiles, tall
OL,17,Ftales, and a depth of love that will
OL,18,Fnever fade."
