OL,6,FSam had been in Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fvisiting his parents for a family
OL,8,Fevent when the accident happened near
OL,9,FCheadle on Monday 26 May.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the makers of Race
OL,12,FAcross The World said: "We are all
OL,13,Fdeeply saddened to hear the tragic
OL,14,Fnews about Sam.
OL,16,F"Everyone who worked with him and
OL,17,Findeed everyone who watched Sam could
OL,18,Fsee just how precious and
OL,19,Ftransformative the trip was for both
OL,20,Fhim and his mum, Jo.
