OL,6,F"Sam embraced the seven-week trip with
OL,7,Fan energy, love and a determination
OL,8,Fthat saw the pair enjoy adventures
OL,9,Facross Mexico to Argentina making
OL,10,Faudiences fall in love with them and
OL,11,Ftheir special bond as a result.
