OL,6,F"Since filming, both Sam and Jo have
OL,7,Fbeen an integral part of the Race
OL,8,FAcross The World cast family, and on
OL,9,Fbehalf of us all from the BBC,
OL,10,Fproduction and the rest of the cast,
OL,11,Fwe would like to extend our deepest
OL,12,Fcondolences to his parents, Andrew and
OL,13,FJo; his brothers, William and Charlie;
OL,14,Fhis step mum Justine; his family and
OL,15,Ffriends."
